{"tid":781564,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一個以前係紙言睇過既故","createTime":"2018-08-16T03:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T04:01:29.000Z","uid":103914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b55f414c4c9beb6068aa2139dcc54acff40c9772","tid":781564,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"岩岩諗起之以前紙言睇過一個故<br />\n而家想睇番 但係唔記得左名 所以想各位巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故事內容大約係：<br />\n<br />\n男主角好似係做運輸 佢揸貨van定貨櫃車 <br />\n一開頭個男主角係酒吧飲左酒  死唔信邪會出事<br />\n點知就撞到個女人<br />\n點知個女人完來係吸血鬼黎  佢要自殺666次先至會死<br />\n之後一路就講個男主角同隻女吸血鬼既故事 有愛情的<br />\n個女吸血鬼好似比男主角稱為八婆玲<br />\n<br />\n之後唔記得發生乜事 個女吸血鬼要咬男主角<br />\n令到男主角都變左吸血鬼 變左男主角都要死666次<br />\n<br />\n最尾結局係個男主角死第666次  之後話終於可以落去見八婆玲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩係紙言 google 同舊登搵極都唔見<br />\n<br />\n想睇下有冇巴打睇過又記得呢個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60199065f071cdd2d17b89a45d0e745bb9f2eb12","tid":781564,"uid":34868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/22861/22862.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F22861%2F22862.html&d=mvgydw%2BwIV3EwqjE35xrrDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6954805f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/22861/22862.html</a>"},{"pid":"c8bd4a6fe70a49d00c9f17ee8168ed67814b5aca","tid":781564,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60199065f071cdd2d17b89a45d0e745bb9f2eb12","tid":781564,"uid":34868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/22861/22862.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F22861%2F22862.html&d=mvgydw%2BwIV3EwqjE35xrrDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6954805f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/22861/22862.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無言感激"}]}